Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,被施压了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.26,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,施压？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,被前辈阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,说是以后不让再报道小红了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是被红绪大人阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:36.02,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 红绪…大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.19,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H575569&\pos(111,350)\b1\bord0}素\N材\N提\N供\N者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.78,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,果 果然是不该那样做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.99,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,有才能的记者是不会向压力屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.24,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,反而会燃起斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.24,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,要比之前更加努力才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.25,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仁子酱 不要啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.42,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,白夜同学怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,比起平常好有压迫感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.55,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他正发愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.56,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,发愁？ 出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:11.18,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 少女般的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.27,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.31,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(362,55)}{\pos(127,180)\shad0\fad(480,0)\c&HAC78EE&}少女般的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.02,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.11,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是关于礼物的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:18.94,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.19,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 白色情人节已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.28,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是春假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.49,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能让小红开心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.16,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.16,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,在白夜能做到的范围内就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.50,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,豪华的东西反而会让人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:43.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(542,0)\frz344.314\c&H2B2226&\move(967,423,990,366,27,5615)\shad0\3c&H9A4A4B&}不\N用\N勉\N强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:43.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz19.192\c&H2B2226&\fad(620,0)\move(335,394,345,402,29,4575)\shad0\3c&H9A4A4B&}可\N做\N到\N的\N范\N围\N内
