Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.17,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.17,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是让你更没头绪了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.43,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真白 你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.19,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.98,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:02.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那又是我们两个一起回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…话题话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.89,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,刘海 不碍事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:33.52,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.68,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,遮着眼睛不碍事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.77,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.02,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.11,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.53,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这倒是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.20,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,这样也挺好的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.04,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,小红平时也很照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.42,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要好好回礼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.84,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,本来是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.88,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,结果不知不觉全都买成巧克力蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.47,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.89,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,路上没人 走近路好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.43,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,反正傍晚也容易混过去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:25.82,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.66,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.32,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.87,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 刚才有谁在那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在的吧 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:41.20,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}没、没 、没有暴露…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.67,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.76,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到飞行类人生物了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞行类人生物？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.76,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,被别人看到你那样很不好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.81,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是被大野同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.98,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想着都傍晚了应该没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.15,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子傍晚一个人走在街上也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.36,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.78,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为遇到怪人或者被卷入犯罪事件就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2E177D&\fad(417,0)\move(62,459,62,421,29,1614)\3c&HBAB0F7&}犯\N罪\N事\N件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2E177D&\fad(417,0)\move(1213,356,1213,397,29,1614)\3c&HBAB0F7&}怪\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.07,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,红绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.74,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全被当作那类人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.50,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.58,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,白 白夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:22.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.08,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.72,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,白夜生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.80,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到真白碳哭着跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.14,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 稍微被白夜训斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.60,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真白碳被训斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.48,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,打击 心碎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.57,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在就是趁虚而入的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.74,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,问我干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.16,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.49,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,以后会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.16,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密暴露了我也不好住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.79,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了怪人就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密暴露了就不能住城里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.76,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,三峰白夜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:20.56,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.89,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,三峰真白同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.65,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.11,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:34.07,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不 比想象中的还要悲惨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.37,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,果然高中的学习太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.33,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,这没办法咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.87,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为实际上是上小学的年纪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.13,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,数学成绩提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.75,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏小红教我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.43,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,白夜同学成绩不也是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.14,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为很聪明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.64,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.35,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,意外的好像不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.56,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,好像还没想到送什么礼物的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.48,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还在烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.11,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,仁子酱 成绩怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.32,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不是问这个的时候啊 木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.40,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.78,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,UMA 那绝对是飞行类人生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,飞行类人生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.66,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.25,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,像人类一样的东西在屋顶飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.50,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,人外生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.25,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,未确认生物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.59,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 嘿……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:36.30,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,仁子酱看到的难道是那个小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:40.60,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我已经是这边的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.27,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不会再变回过去的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「这边」是哪边！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.52,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,仁子酱冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.95,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,请你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.28,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,小红的取材暂时放过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.62,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有更好的题材了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不会给小红添麻烦了倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.80,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有更好的题材了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.80,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会找小红了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.84,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.93,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.94,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2F2C33&\shad0\move(226,533,247,533,0,2234)}怎\N么\N说\N才\N好\N呢   \N\N说\N不\N出\N口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为小红是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,突然间说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.03,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.78,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.75,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.33,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那么说我真是碍事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.42,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.17,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真的就是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:55.96,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.93,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,又…又不是因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.22,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我尊敬的可是红绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.60,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,随你们搞好关系就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.01,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,约会之类的全部都搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.18,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,相亲相爱就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.39,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.65,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.61,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个想法可以有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.07,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.03,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.65,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.45,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是白夜请客
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.88,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,又是这么多尼斯湖水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:45.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,这个零食公司对尼斯湖水怪有什么样的执着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.93,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,关于明天那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.93,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真白有什么想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.02,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:56.11,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 那是你们两个去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.40,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我想真白可能也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.03,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.20,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,现在一想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.49,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,好像一直都没有带你们参观过这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.62,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.88,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那么先想一想想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.00,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.67,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是电灯泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:30.64,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,小红不会把真白放家里然后去玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.98,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.52,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你想要一个人在家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.36,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.94,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要带我去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.28,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.91,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.28,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是春假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,各种小孩子的电影也在上映
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.54,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.21,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我有想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.04,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.92,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H68EAF1&\3c&H2B2D41&\shad0\frz24.461\pos(14,237)\fad(400,0)}我的儿子\N被宇宙人抓走\N很是头疼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.26,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 大家要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.59,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,没听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.89,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天没机会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.60,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.52,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,红绪 快一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.73,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去帮忙义卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.69,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙幼稚园慈善拍卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.15,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要早点去然后做准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.61,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.49,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,等… 为什么变成那样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.99,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.78,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,这是白色情人节的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.16,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.58,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,带着小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.25,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的去玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.51,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不同意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.51,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,只是去看电影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.43,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.01,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有带白夜和真白在这附近玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.68,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:56.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不高兴所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.40,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,准备让我等到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.65,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,给我够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.07,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.98,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.28,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:09.91,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不同意的啊！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.83,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 姐姐大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.45,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.08,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说从没想过能瞒过她出门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.71,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,白夜也觉得看电影就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.05,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有约会的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.30,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.39,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这一部…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.02,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.48,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,447)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4E312D&\shad0\blur3}才\N、\N才\N没\N有\N什\N么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.23,weiqueren,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,447)\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\blur4}才\N、\N才\N没\N有\N什\N么
